  "summary": "If you're craving crispy, spicy chicken with minimal effort, this Nashville Hot Air Fryer Chicken Legs recipe is perfect for you. These air fryer chicken legs deliver all the bold flavours of classic fried chicken, but with less oil and mess. Coated in a fiery mix of smoked paprika, cayenne pepper, and garlic powder, the chicken legs develop a crispy skin that rivals deep-fried alternatives. The airfryer method ensures even cooking, leaving the chicken tender and juicy inside while perfectly crispy outside. Whether you’re serving them with fries, a fresh salad, or dipping in honey mustard, this recipe for air fryer chicken legs makes for a quick and delicious dinner. Pair it with your favourite sides like coleslaw or roasted vegetables for a satisfying meal with a spicy kick.",
